title: Spare Phone 5 WiFi Voice Calls v1.01
description:
VoIP phone calls with your Google Voice account on any Android device. 

Free unlimited calls to phones in the USA and Canada when used over a wireless connection.

Features:

* Multiple account support
* Wireless, 3G, 4G support
* Native dialer integration with call filters
* Bluetooth support
* Custom status messages
* DTMF touch tones
* 7 digit dialing support
* Quick access to voice mail
* Incoming and outgoing phone calls
* Swipe interface allows easy navigation

Beta features:

* Manage your forwarding phones
* Request call backs

Requirements:

1.) Any Android device(including Wi-Fi only tablets and out of service phones).
2.) Google Voice account. If you need an account simply visit: https://www.google.com/voice
